title: Udan Pirappu
subTitle: Best friends Sathya and Viji are against selling their colony to a land grabber. Their friendship is put to the test after Viji falls in love with Sumathi and marries her.

title: Thedinen Vanthathu
subTitle: A man and his friend try to save a bag containing a hefty sum, which they hide in an empty house. When they return for the bag, the house is occupied by a girl and her family.

title: Kuppathu Raja
subTitle: Rocket, a slum dweller, sees his life change when he joins forces with a gang leader MG Rajendran to put a stop to crime in their area.

title: Pattikattu Ponniah
subTitle: A farmer heads to the city to find a way to pay off his father's debts. However, things take an unexpected twist when he turns to wrestling as a profession.

title: Sakthi Leelai
subTitle: Sage Bhringi worships only Lord Shiva, Brahma and Vishnu. When Goddess Parvati stands in his way, he goes to the extent of giving rise to a demon.

title: Vellore Mavattam
subTitle: Muthukumar becomes an IPS officer and is posted in his own district. In spite of facing problems from the local politicians for being honest, he vows to change the corrupt system.

title: Thaali Kattiya Raasa
subTitle: Mythili falls in love with Pandian, the educated man of her village. However, they have to first deal with Mythili's cruel father who once ruined her sister's life.

title: Diwan
